==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[conventional]], [[formulaic]], and [[oversimplified]] [[conception]], [[opinion]], or [[image]].
# A person who is regarded as [[embody]]ing or [[conform]]ing to a set [[image]] or [[type]].
# (''printing'') A [[metal]] [[printing]] [[plate]] [[cast]] from a [[matrix]] [[mould]]ed from a [[raise]]d printing [[surface]].

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|stereotyp|e}}

# {{transitive}}: To make a stereotype of someone or something, or [[characterize]] someone by a stereotype.
# {{transitive}}: To [[print]] from a stereotype.

